        <abstract> 
<p>The first half of vol. 2 of <hi rend="italic">Variation</hi> is printed.</p> 
            <p>News of his marriage.</p>
            <p>Sends portraits of Russian scientists.</p>
            <p>Hopes CD will write his book on man and asks permission to translate it.</p>
            <p>Moving to Germany for two or three years.</p>
        </abstract>
